dozens of innocent lives?

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:28.319
Who saw it?

00:07:29.439 --> 00:07:30.560
What proof do you have?

00:07:30.759 --> 00:07:32.199
Who would dare accuse Prince Duan?

00:07:36.839 --> 00:07:38.120
You're powerless

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.600
and being ridiculous.

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:41.600
At worst,

00:07:41.600 --> 00:07:43.120
Prince Duan and his son will be exiled.

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:44.920
