00:07:45.199 --> 00:07:47.000
His Majesty will call him back.

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:49.000
But taking your life

00:07:49.839 --> 00:07:51.839
is easier than pinching an ant.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:56.959
I'd like to see

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:00.120
who can save you today.

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:02.600
Go.

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:05.160
Kill her.

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:11.759
Yu,

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:13.480
don't you like

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:14.919
watching women dance?

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:17.000
I practiced this dance so hard

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.679
that my feet swelled.

00:09:19.759 --> 00:09:20.919
Why don't you like it?

00:09:21.480 --> 00:09:22.960
What did you do to Xi Yan?

00:09:26.159 --> 00:09:26.840
She's dead.

00:09:28.759 --> 00:09:29.919
If she were dead,

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:32.440
you wouldn't be scheming this much.

00:09:44.559 --> 00:09:45.360
Remember.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:48.600
If anything happens to her,
you'll be buried with her.

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:53.240
I'll be buried with her?

00:09:55.759 --> 00:09:57.240
Did you forget, Yu?

00:09:58.840 --> 00:10:00.879
When I was little,
my father was murdered.

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:05.039
The enemy wanted me dead too.

00:10:07.679 --> 00:10:10.000
You were the one who saved me.

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:15.480
Why?

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:18.679
Why can't you protect me

00:10:18.679 --> 00:10:20.799
as you did back then?

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:29.279
I'm warning you.

00:10:30.039 --> 00:10:32.080
If you lay a finger on Xi Yan again,

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.240
hurt her even a little,

00:10:35.159 --> 00:10:36.679
and I'll take it back tenfold.

00:10:38.919 --> 00:10:40.000
Understand?

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:52.600
Yu!

00:11:05.799 --> 00:11:06.360
Your Highness.

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.200
Your Highness,

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:08.720
what happened?

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:09.639
Your Highness.

00:11:10.759 --> 00:11:14.159
He wants to kill me for her.

00:11:16.639 --> 00:11:17.639
He doesn't care

00:11:19.679 --> 00:11:22.320
about me at all.

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:25.879
Your Highness.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.399
Just why?

00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:36.120
You have fifteen minutes.

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:43.639
Don't worry, Father.

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:45.559
I've arranged everything.

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.200
Those ministers at court

00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:48.679
will all speak for us

00:11:48.799 --> 00:11:50.200
in front of His Majesty.

00:11:51.570 --> 00:11:53.840
I'm the non-imperial prince
appointed by the late Emperor.

00:11:54.679 --> 00:11:56.200
I've rendered

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:57.399
countless merits.

00:11:57.399 --> 00:11:59.039
His Majesty won't punish me.

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:00.879
You don't need to fawn over anyone.

00:12:01.840 --> 00:12:02.759
I was only reminded of

00:12:02.759 --> 00:12:04.159
General Li.

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:05.080
They said

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:06.360
he had too many achievements,

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:07.080
that's why...

00:12:12.879 --> 00:12:14.120
But it's nothing serious.

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:14.679
In the end,

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:16.960
